        "body": "## Summary\n- add the Anthropic Sandbox Runtime provider as canonical `sandbox-runtime` with alias `srt`\n- keep v1 as a local one-shot delegated-run provider with no persistent lease semantics\n- wire config, env overrides, docs, tests, and live sandbox enforcement smoke coverage\n\nRefs: #267\n\n## Verification\n- `go test ./internal/cli ./internal/providers/sandboxruntime ./internal/providers/all`\n- `go test ./...`\n- `go vet ./...`\n- `go build -trimpath -o bin/crabbox ./cmd/crabbox`\n- `go test -race ./...`\n- `bin/crabbox providers --json` provider contract check\n- `bin/crabbox doctor --provider sandbox-runtime`\n- `bin/crabbox run --provider sandbox-runtime -- echo ok`\n- `node scripts/live-sandbox-runtime-smoke.test.js`\n- `node scripts/build-docs-site.mjs`\n- `scripts/live-sandbox-runtime-smoke.sh`\n- `autoreview --mode branch --base origin/main` clean after addressing one test-harness finding",
